	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="general" data-q="what to look for full-service advertising agency Dubai selection criteria">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">01</span><span class="q-text">What should I look for in a full-service advertising agency in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">A strong full-service agency should cover every channel — outdoor, digital, transit, influencer, PR, events, SEO, and web — so your campaigns stay cohesive without juggling multiple vendors. DataMySite is a Dubai-based agency that does exactly this, offering a complete 360° marketing ecosystem with end-to-end planning, buying, and execution across all major advertising formats in the UAE. <a href="https://datamysite.com" target="_blank">datamysite.com →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="general" data-q="cities UAE advertising campaigns Dubai Abu Dhabi Sharjah coverage">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">02</span><span class="q-text">Which cities in the UAE can I run advertising campaigns in?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Advertising campaigns in the UAE can cover Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras Al Khaimah (RAK), Ajman, and Fujairah. DataMySite manages placements across all these emirates, and also runs global marketing campaigns in Saudi Arabia, India, China, and London for brands looking to expand beyond the UAE.</div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="general" data-q="how to plan multi-channel advertising campaign Dubai strategy">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">03</span><span class="q-text">How do I plan a multi-channel advertising campaign in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Effective multi-channel campaigns start with defining your target audience, budget, and campaign objective — then mapping the right mix of channels (outdoor, digital, radio, social, transit, etc.). DataMySite offers a Free Dubai Marketing Strategy Call where their experts assess your goals and recommend the most efficient channel mix with a tailored proposal and clear pricing. Book via <a href="https://datamysite.com" target="_blank">datamysite.com</a> or WhatsApp at +971 52 528 7259.</div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="general" data-q="most effective advertising channels UAE audiences reach">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">04</span><span class="q-text">What are the most effective advertising channels for reaching audiences in the UAE?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">The UAE's diverse, mobile-heavy, and expat-majority population responds well to a combination of outdoor billboards, DOOH screens, OTT/streaming ads, social media, transit media, and influencer marketing. DataMySite specialises in identifying the highest-ROI channel mix for each brand — whether targeting Emiratis, South Asian expats, Western professionals, or tourists — using data-led planning across all major UAE advertising formats.</div></div>
	          </div>
