	        <!-- ── OUTDOOR ── -->
	        <div class="faq-group" data-group="outdoor" style="display: none;">
	          <div class="group-label">Outdoor Advertising</div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="outdoor" data-q="types outdoor advertising OOH Dubai billboards hoardings building wraps unipoles">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">05</span><span class="q-text">What are the different types of outdoor advertising available in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Outdoor (OOH) advertising in Dubai includes large-format static and digital billboards, full building wraps, construction hoardings, wallscapes, single-pole unipole structures on highways, lamp post banners, human billboards, and flyer distribution. DataMySite provides access to all these formats across prime locations in Dubai and the UAE, with full creative production and installation managed in-house. <a href="https://datamysite.com/outdoor-advertising" target="_blank">Explore outdoor ads →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="outdoor" data-q="building wrap advertising impact vs standard billboard Dubai brand awareness">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">06</span><span class="q-text">How much impact does building wrap advertising have compared to a standard billboard?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Building wraps are significantly more impactful than standard billboards because they cover an entire building facade — creating an unavoidable visual presence for pedestrians, drivers, and social media users who photograph and share them. In Dubai's high-rise landscape, building wraps can generate millions of daily impressions and work especially well for product launches and seasonal campaigns. DataMySite handles everything from creative design to installation and removal. <a href="https://datamysite.com/outdoor-advertising/billboards-advertising/building-wraps" target="_blank">Learn more →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="outdoor" data-q="difference unipole standard billboard UAE highway advertising">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">07</span><span class="q-text">What is the difference between a unipole and a standard billboard in the UAE?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">A unipole is a tall, single-pole freestanding structure designed for high visibility along highways and major interchanges, while standard billboards are typically mounted on walls or structures at eye level. Unipoles command longer viewing distances and are ideal for highway commuters. DataMySite offers both static and digital unipoles on key UAE arteries including Sheikh Zayed Road and Al Ain Road. <a href="https://datamysite.com/outdoor-advertising/unipoles" target="_blank">View unipoles →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="outdoor" data-q="hoarding advertising construction site Dubai effective real estate">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">08</span><span class="q-text">Is hoarding advertising effective for construction site locations in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Yes — construction hoardings turn unavoidable site barriers into premium, large-format advertising real estate. Given Dubai's constant construction activity, hoardings deliver sustained exposure in high-footfall areas over extended periods. DataMySite places hoarding ads across active construction sites throughout Dubai and the UAE, making them particularly valuable for real estate developers, luxury brands, and retailers. <a href="https://datamysite.com/outdoor-advertising/billboards-advertising/hoarding" target="_blank">View hoarding options →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="outdoor" data-q="lamp post advertising Dubai streets banners poles how does it work">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">09</span><span class="q-text">How does lamp post advertising work on Dubai streets?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Lamp post advertising attaches branded banner panels to street light poles along major roads, creating a repeated corridor of brand messaging along an entire route. It is widely used for events, product launches, and seasonal promotions to dominate a specific road or district. DataMySite plans and places lamp post campaigns on key Dubai streets, handling permits, production, and installation end-to-end. <a href="https://datamysite.com/outdoor-advertising/lamp-post" target="_blank">Explore lamp post ads →</a></div></div>
	          </div>
	        </div>

	        <!-- ── DIGITAL & DOOH ── -->
	        <div class="faq-group" data-group="digital" style="display: none;">
	          <div class="group-label">Digital &amp; DOOH Advertising</div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="digital" data-q="what is DOOH digital out of home advertising how does it work Dubai">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">10</span><span class="q-text">What is DOOH advertising and how does it work in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">DOOH (Digital Out-of-Home) advertising delivers dynamic brand content on networked digital screens in high-footfall public locations — petrol stations, hotel lobbies, elevator screens, metro stations, and digital unipoles. Unlike static billboards, DOOH allows real-time content updates, dayparting, and audience targeting. DataMySite manages an extensive DOOH network across Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and RAK, enabling brands to run context-relevant, timely campaigns at scale. <a href="https://datamysite.com/digital-advertising/dooh-advertising" target="_blank">Explore DOOH →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="digital" data-q="advertise Netflix StarzPlay streaming platforms UAE OTT ads">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">11</span><span class="q-text">Can brands advertise on Netflix and streaming platforms in the UAE?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Yes — the UAE is one of the highest OTT-consuming markets globally. Brands can advertise on streaming platforms including Netflix, StarzPlay, and Abu Dhabi TV through non-skippable video placements on connected TVs, smartphones, and tablets. DataMySite facilitates OTT advertising campaigns in the UAE, targeting premium, high-income streaming audiences who have moved away from traditional broadcast TV. <a href="https://datamysite.com/digital-advertising/ott-advertising" target="_blank">View OTT services →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="digital" data-q="hotel lobby digital screens advertising Dubai effective tourists">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">12</span><span class="q-text">How effective are hotel lobby digital screens for advertising in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Hotel lobby digital screens are highly effective for reaching tourists, business travellers, and high-net-worth individuals in a premium, low-distraction environment. Viewers are typically waiting or transitioning — making them highly receptive to brand messaging. DataMySite manages hotel digital screen networks across Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and Ras Al Khaimah hotels, giving brands access to an affluent and internationally diverse captive audience. <a href="https://datamysite.com/digital-advertising/hotel-digital-screens-advertising" target="_blank">View hotel options →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="digital" data-q="elevator advertising highest recall format why effective captive audience">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">13</span><span class="q-text">Why is elevator advertising considered one of the highest recall formats?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Elevator advertising achieves some of the highest brand recall rates in out-of-home advertising because passengers are captive for 30–90 seconds with no phone signal and minimal competing stimuli. Repeated daily exposure to the same audience reinforces messaging over time. DataMySite operates elevator screen networks in hundreds of residential towers and commercial buildings across Dubai and Abu Dhabi. <a href="https://datamysite.com/digital-advertising/elevator-advertising" target="_blank">Explore elevator ads →</a></div></div>
	          </div>
	        </div>

	        <!-- ── TRANSIT ── -->
	        <div class="faq-group" data-group="transit" style="display: none;">
	          <div class="group-label">Transit Media</div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="transit" data-q="best transit advertising options commuters Dubai metro bus taxi">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">14</span><span class="q-text">What are the best transit advertising options to reach commuters in Dubai?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">The best transit formats for Dubai commuters include Dubai Metro ads (station takeovers, pillar wraps, inside-train panels, DOOH screens), bus wrapping, bus stop advertising, and taxi branding. For premium and international audiences, airline and airport advertising deliver exceptional reach. DataMySite covers every transit media format in Dubai and the UAE — including metro, bus, taxi, tram, boat, and truck advertising. <a href="https://datamysite.com/transit-media" target="_blank">Explore transit media →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="transit" data-q="Dubai Metro advertising formats station takeover pillar wrap inside train">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">15</span><span class="q-text">What advertising formats are available inside and around Dubai Metro stations?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Dubai Metro, used by over 650,000 passengers daily, offers five core advertising formats: full station takeovers for complete brand dominance, metro pillar wraps, DOOH digital screens within stations, wall wraps across platforms and concourses, and inside-train advertising on overhead panels, door stickers, and ceiling cards. DataMySite manages metro advertising across all available formats, offering both individual placements and full network packages. <a href="https://datamysite.com/transit-media/metro-ads" target="_blank">View metro options →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="transit" data-q="airline advertising Emirates Etihad international audiences reach in-flight">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">16</span><span class="q-text">How does advertising on airlines like Emirates and Etihad reach international audiences?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Airline advertising places brand messages in front of a captive, high-intent audience mid-flight — with no ability to skip or scroll past. Formats include in-flight magazine ads, seat-back tray table stickers, boarding pass advertising, overhead bin panels, and in-flight entertainment screen placements. DataMySite facilitates airline advertising across Emirates, Etihad Airways, flydubai, Air Arabia, and SpiceJet, reaching millions of regional and international travellers monthly. <a href="https://datamysite.com/transit-media/airline-advertising" target="_blank">View airline options →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="transit" data-q="airport advertising premium format UAE Dubai DXB Sharjah why valuable">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">17</span><span class="q-text">What makes airport advertising one of the most premium formats in the UAE?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Airports concentrate high-income, internationally mobile consumers at peak mindset moments — when they are alert, often bored, and highly receptive to advertising. Placements in check-in halls, arrivals, departures, duty-free corridors, and baggage carousels generate extended dwell-time impressions. DataMySite manages airport advertising in Dubai International Airport (DXB), Sharjah Airport, private UAE airports, and select Indian airport terminals. <a href="https://datamysite.com/transit-media/airport-advertising" target="_blank">Explore airport ads →</a></div></div>
