	        <!-- ── INFLUENCER & CELEBRITY ── -->
	        <div class="faq-group" data-group="influencer" style="display: none;">
	          <div class="group-label">Influencer &amp; Celebrity Marketing</div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="influencer" data-q="benefits influencer marketing brands UAE Dubai social media ROI">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">18</span><span class="q-text">What are the benefits of influencer marketing for brands in the UAE?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Influencer marketing in the UAE generates authentic, community-trusted brand exposure at a fraction of traditional media costs. With one of the highest social media usage rates globally, UAE consumers heavily rely on influencer recommendations. DataMySite manages full influencer campaigns across nano (1K–10K), micro (10K–100K), and macro (100K–1M) tiers on Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, and Snapchat — handling sourcing, contracts, briefs, content approval, and performance reporting. <a href="https://datamysite.com/influencer-marketing" target="_blank">Learn more →</a></div></div>
	          </div>

	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="influencer" data-q="Bollywood sports celebrities brand growth Middle East UAE GCC endorsements">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">19</span><span class="q-text">How can Bollywood and sports celebrities help a brand grow in the Middle East?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Celebrity endorsements create instant credibility and mass emotional association with a brand. In the UAE, where South Asian expats form the largest demographic group, Bollywood celebrities carry enormous influence. Sports personalities similarly drive strong engagement among sports fans across the GCC. DataMySite connects brands with both Bollywood celebrities and sports personalities for ambassador campaigns, event appearances, and social media collaborations tailored to the UAE market. <a href="https://datamysite.com/celebrity-marketing" target="_blank">Explore celebrity marketing →</a></div></div>
