	          <div class="faq-item" data-cat="influencer" data-q="difference nano micro macro influencers which best ROI brand UAE">
	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">20</span><span class="q-text">What is the difference between nano, micro, and macro influencers — and which delivers best ROI?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Nano influencers (1K–10K) deliver the highest engagement rates and authentic trust — ideal for niche or hyperlocal campaigns. Micro influencers (10K–100K) balance engagement with broader reach, perfect for lifestyle, F&amp;B, fashion, and tech brands. Macro influencers (100K–1M) maximise awareness for large-scale campaigns. DataMySite advises on the optimal tier mix based on your budget, sector, and campaign goal — often combining all three for maximum efficiency. <a href="https://datamysite.com/influencer-marketing" target="_blank">View influencer tiers →</a></div></div>
