	            <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false"><div class="faq-q-inner"><span class="q-num">23</span><span class="q-text">How does brand sponsorship work and what are the benefits in the UAE?</span></div><div class="faq-tog"><span></span><span></span></div></button>
	            <div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Sponsorship aligns your brand with an event, team, or property that your target audience already loves — borrowing their credibility and emotional engagement. Benefits include sustained logo visibility, audience association, press coverage, and social media amplification. DataMySite facilitates corporate sponsorships (conferences, sporting events, community initiatives) and entertainment sponsorships (music festivals, cultural events, experiential activations) across the UAE and GCC. <a href="https://datamysite.com/sponsorships" target="_blank">View sponsorship packages →</a></div></div>
